== Notes ==

On March 31st 2014 we lost the Godfather Of House Music, Frankie Knuckles. To celebrate his life and music we present two previously unheard mixes, both recorded in 2011. The first mix was recorded live on the turntables at a special event in Shoreditch, London. The second is a studio session from the same year, showcasing his unique talent as a DJ, producer and remixer.

== Notes ==

This week's Essential Mix rounds up some of the best DJ sets from Scotland's most beautiful dance event Rockness. The focus is on the Annie Mac and Soma Afterburner stages with sets from Scottish born producer, remixer and songwriter Burns, Glasgow based techno star Gary Beck and a sensational sixty minutes from Club 75 (Busy P, DJ Mehdi, Cassius and Justice).
